{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 5,
  "title": "第五章（用中）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天地不仁 以萬物為芻狗 聖人不仁 以百姓為芻狗"
    },
    {
      "text": "天地之間 亓猶橐籥與 虛而不淈 動而俞出"
    },
    {
      "text": "多聞數窮 不若守於中"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地生萬物，人最為貴，天地視之如芻草狗畜，不貴望其報也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人愛養萬民，不以仁恩，法天地行自然。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人視百姓如芻草狗畜，不貴望其禮意。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地之間空虛，和氣流行，故萬物自生。人能除情慾，節滋味，清五臟，則神明居之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "橐籥中空虛，人能有聲氣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言空虛無有屈竭時，動搖之，益出聲氣也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "多事害神，多言害身，口開舌舉，必有禍患。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不如守德於中，育養精神，愛氣希言。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人與天地合其德，以百姓比芻狗也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "橐，排橐也。籥，樂籥也。橐籥之中空洞，無情無為，故虛而不得窮屈，動而不可竭盡也。天地之中，蕩然任自然，故不可得而窮，猶若橐籥也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "愈為之則愈失之矣。物樹其惡，事錯其言，不慧不濟，不言不理，必窮之數也。橐籥而守數中，則無窮盡，棄己任物，則莫不理。若橐籥有意於為聲也，則不足以共吹者之求也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
